node.text:
Another fantastic day done, here's how the medal table stands after Day 8!

Pictures are:
1 - Daniel Dias waving his left arm poolside 🇧🇷
2 - Megan Hollander reaching very low for a badminton return. 🇳🇱
3 - David Smith, boccia player with blue and red hair roaring out loud. 🇬🇧
4 - Sarah Aljumaah gets ready to throw the shot. 🇸🇦
5 - Rory Mead racing in a hand cycle. 🇳🇿
6 - Yiting Shi in mid-air racing to the finish line.🇨🇳
7 - Greg Stewart during a mid shot-put throw 🇨🇦
8 - Johannes Nambala on the track striding out. 🇳🇦

#Paralympics #Tokyo2020

Today #badminton made its #paralympics debut! 👏🏻😍
